Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'm still your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suspect it wasn't an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to uncover the snowman trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:10.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:59.51,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Last time, Professor Agasa took us\Non a trip a snowy mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,While Genta and the others were making a snowman,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:07.65,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,they met a group from a nearby art college,\Nwho were doing their graduation project.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, when we went looking for Kokura\NSakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} outside of the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found her floating in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, let's head up there where she probably fell from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may find some traces of the accident there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Accident"? It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone about to meet their friends for lunch in an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't drag a snowboard out in a snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this is a murder, the criminal is likely among those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:02.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is how they got Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the way down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To throw her in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Unsmashable Snowman, Part Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably where she fell from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even though the fence is broken, all that's left is the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was told it broke last week and was scheduled to be fixed soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any snowboard tracks here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably got covered by the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A snowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:46.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be the one you were talking\Nabout, your graduation project?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:48.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Itabashi Kazuya (22)\N\hUniversity Student\h
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, while you were making this, Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Ndid you hear her voice or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were pretty close to where she fell from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I was up here until 1:00, right before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was focusing on finishing this, and the snowstorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was pretty loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So... What exactly is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's a snow model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:24.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the only one who knows\Nhow close it is to being finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:24.23,CharCard01,,0,0,0,,\hOnoue Asaka (22)\h\N\hUniversity Student\h
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:24.23,CharCard02,,0,0,0,,\h\hKiyama Tanji (22)\h\h\N\hUniversity Student\h
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He keeps it all in his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A snow model, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even I can tell it's unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, over there, you have an apple, bananas, and{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} tan{\r}gerines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys were gonna use these later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those were parts to our snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its head fell off due to the snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:52.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:05:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stomping around, our Detective\NBadges are buried down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to put gloves on sticks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G...Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your nose... Your nose is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This should do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now listen:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lie face down and stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, so amazing! You're like a nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, this is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm jealous of you, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't believe you got a nosebleed from falling on snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A scoop must have been buried under there, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It definitely wasn't a scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did taste something funny though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A funny taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta! What'd it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The snow! What'd it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a bit salty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.69,0:06:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The autopsy revealed that the water\Nfrom the lake was found in her stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it really was an accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is actually more proof to the contrary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:58.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These tracks the criminal left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, there are some things left unclarified...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're just about ready to wrap up and head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The chief invited you over for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it'd be great if I were invited...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if there's any doubt, be sure to investigate thoroughly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ce of this being deliberate is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.53,0:07:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm 120% sure this was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may not have been an accident after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, what's up, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just called us out here suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already told you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko's death was an accident, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but, this guy has something strange to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, nothing strange about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko wasn't in an accident; she was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the criminal is one of you three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey now, I only got everyone out here because\NI thought you had a clue about the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not so you could call people murderers like a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we look at everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can only conclude Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} snowboarded\Nthrough the place where the fence should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:50.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the snowstorm, I know she\Ndrowned after falling in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I say this because l known no one else came toward the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:09:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since the bridge was blocked until we police arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, there are about ten meters\Nfrom the lake to the bottom of the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if she were pushed from the cliff,\Nshe wouldn't make it to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, there's one last thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One hour after she parted with those\Nthree, she failed to show up for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, they searched for her until...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,-Until- her body was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with the use of a rope, one of them couldn't get\Nher body down there and make it back in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't be telling me that any of them could possibly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this is quicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just too upset with myself to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe so simple a trick fooled me this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A trick, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the criminal pushed Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} off the cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After putting her in something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Put her in something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey you're not gonna say she was put in a sled, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you put her in a sled...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd flip over, just like a snowboard would.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if someone rode down in the sled with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would still have to climb back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A sled? It's nothing so unusable as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:11:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I speak of something that will definitely arrive\Nat the lake and will disappear with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arrive there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way, nothing's that convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead of using misleading words\Nsuch as "arrive" and "disappear,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suggest using "roll to" and "melt".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's more straight to the point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it's something we've assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Assembled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something we've assembled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:39.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course it's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you put that woman in a giant snowball, put it at the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And roll it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll roll down and make a huge splash when it hits the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't take long for the snow to melt, which\Nwould leave Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} floating in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That does make sense, since the hot\Nsprings make the water unusually hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A snowman? Quit joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know Sakuko was pretty small, but..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'd be able to fit a normal sized person in a snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would break apart before making it to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, it would have to be at least two meters to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if someone did get so much snow together,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think they could push it off alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But see, a lot of snow isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, it just has to be as big as...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As big as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:45.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The snowman I'm leaning against.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it were only that big...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd break apart before reaching the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sounds right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this supposed to be funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just reminding you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of when Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} fell near the snowman earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ended up with a nosebleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G...Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your nose... Your nose is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, do you remember what the snow was like then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, the crucial point of the trick is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:53.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:14:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. He used the chemical reaction\Nof the salt to harden the snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.99,0:14:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chemical reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When salt comes in contact with snow, the freezing\Npoint is lowered, making that part of the snow melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But before it melts, it absorbs the nearby heat,\Ncausing the snow around it to freeze and harden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When freezing is needed for skiing\Ncourses and igloos, the do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But for ski courses, ammonium sulfate is used\Nto prevent damage after the snow melts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ammonium sulfate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ammonium... sulfate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll learn about it in your future science classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, all of this means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where was this supposed snowball hardened at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:14:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see it, but it probably was done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right at this snowman near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hardening of the snowball was done here,\Nleaving the snow around it hardened as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} got a nosebleed after falling here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Was" done there? Isn't it still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit made this snowman quickly\Nafter committing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To prevent us from realizing this snowman was used for the trick,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the culprit made another body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the proof is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:37.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the head is hardened with salt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as you recreate the shape, you\Ncan place the head on the body again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the one who put Sakuko in the snowball was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, the person who was making a\Nsnowman the entire time: Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who could've pulled this off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even to just putting the head on a\Nnew body requires concise work,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which is something only the creator, Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, you took advantage of the\Nsnowstorm and called her outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before, you told her to wear her skiing gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Since the snowstorm's getting bad, let's talk in the room."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after luring her to your room...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You forced her head into the sink...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Effectively drowning her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:51.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then put her boots on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,went out into the snowstorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put her into the space you had prepared earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then put her snowboard inside,\Nand then put on a lid made of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then rolled it up to the edge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pushed it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with that, she was floating in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But hold on, can all of that be done in an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he supposedly rolled Sakuko and the snowball off the cliff,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he made another snowball for the body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he came to meet with us, he\Nwasn't breathing hard or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true, he'd be tired if he made another, but\Nif he uses one that's already half finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Half?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all probably had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the kids did something to their\Nsnowman in order to surprise you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, we did it to order to surprise them later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the body of our snowman, we planted...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our Detective Badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's the sound of our Detective Badges...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's coming from their snowman's stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, our snowman's head didn't fall off during the snowstorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:38.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just removed the fruits and used its parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,allowing him to use it to make another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But that's not proof Itabashi's the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The evidence centers around Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:58.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the autopsy results, the water\Nfrom the lake was found in her stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, in his room, you should find containers\Nor traces of water he prepared before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may even find a sample of her hair as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, her sink could've been used,\Nbut Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s is more likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:27.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it had happened in her room, he would have put on her\Ngoggles, gloves, and her hat before putting her in the snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itabashi had no reason to kill Sakuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I had it in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because of Asaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, I just somehow did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itabashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, right? That Sakuko loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you always loved Asaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The girl who gracefully scaled the slopes with her skis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make you forget about Asaka, that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Made Asaka go snowboarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knew she was too inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She stole Asaka's legs that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All for such a stupid reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was muttering about it when she was drunk once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is something wrong, Sakuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I broke Asaka's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.84,0:20:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've done everything I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she just won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's her deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asaka, that bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:21:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you'd care that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itabashi, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me about this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itabashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only because I didn't want to give my enemy salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, I couldn't be sure what you\Nwould have done to her if you had known.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Avenge Asaka and get covered in mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't let you have that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think putting salt on snow makes it harden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not just for hardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you put salt on snow and mix them, the salt disperses...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:32.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until it's all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They use this same method for melting snow\Non the road, using calcium chloride.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:43.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, that guy used salt wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wrong way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.95,0:23:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The worst way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of melting his murderous desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hardened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A biting turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biting turtle and 1,000,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.63,0:24:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps these two cases have a connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mysterious Case Near the Pond
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.10,0:24:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,X-ray
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.10,0:24:41.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
